Job Description

  Deliver memorable moments to customers
  Assist in customer service @ kiosk / dining area
  Obtain feedback from guests and improve future experience
  Maintain guest relations and log book
  Train / buddy new service staff

Industry Background &amp; Skills

  Possess at least 1 year relevant experience in the same capacity
  Good communication and interpersonal skills
  Positive mindset and a passion in providing excellent guest service.
  Good team-player andhave the ability to prioritize in a fast-paced environment
